text: Dirty Diamonds is the 25th studio album by Alice Cooper and was released on 4 July, 2005 internationally and 2 August, 2005 in the United States. It went to number 169 in the United States and number 89 in the United Kingdom. It was his highest charting album since 1994. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2005 albums Category:Alice Cooper albums
